## guide:// URI Scheme

This project exposes content via the `guide://` URI scheme, listed in MCP `resources/list`.

### Content URIs
- `guide://expression` — retrieve content by category or collection name
- `guide://expression/pattern` — retrieve content filtered by glob pattern

### Command URIs
- `guide://_command` — execute a server command
- `guide://_command/args` — command with positional arguments
- `guide://_command/args?key=value` — command with keyword arguments

### Resolution
- Prefer MCP resource discovery and direct resource reads when the client supports them.
- Use the `read_resource` tool as a fallback for clients that only expose tools.
